dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Kenosha County, WI 2019
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and Right Of Ways (ROW) for Kenosha County, Wisconsin in 2019 and includes the layers 'Kenosha_Roads_2019' and 'Kenosha_ROW_2019'.ROW: [Kenosha County Cadastral Line Features. Contains all lines for COX - Condominium Boundary Lines, CSX - CSM Boundary Lines, EAX - Easement Lines, PLX - Parcel Lines, RWX - ROW Lines, SDX - Subdivision Boundary Lines, TMX - Tie Mark Lines, TRX - Text Related Leader Lines.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
